Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.36,0:03:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是老樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.90,0:03:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\pos(235,270)\fs20\fad(600,500)}究極的豆腐店漂移
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.30,0:03:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,91年款要一百三十萬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.05,0:03:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,S13真貴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.27,0:03:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是86吧 86還現實點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.78,0:03:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之車一定得是FR
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.99,0:03:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對吧? 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.46,0:03:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.44,0:03:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在聽嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.44,0:03:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在聽呢 樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.64,0:03:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼86要多少錢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.84,0:03:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三十萬能買到 但不包驗車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.61,0:03:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在存了多少?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.11,0:03:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五萬多點...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.77,0:03:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差得遠呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.63,0:03:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找不到快速賺錢的辦法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.16,0:04:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,憑現在加油站打工賺的錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.63,0:04:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干一整個暑假也只有十二萬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.22,0:04:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有薪水高點的活了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.42,0:04:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海 你們在打工?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.91,0:04:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茂木...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.00,0:04:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.79,0:04:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和你們說話有那麼意外?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.30,0:04:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪有...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.74,0:04:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說干一整個暑假也只有十二萬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.37,0:04:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一天要工作幾小時?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.78,0:04:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從早做到晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.30,0:04:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼辛苦 一個月才十二萬?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.98,0:04:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一般都是這樣的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.60,0:04:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高中生打工薪水低得可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.67,0:04:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還真不知道...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.50,0:04:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我從沒打過工...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.49,0:04:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打工加油哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.21,0:04:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,期末考試後一起去玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.78,0:04:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她剛才說一起去玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.32,0:05:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和茂木一起?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.38,0:05:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好極 好極
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.82,0:05:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海你怎麼不告訴我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.94,0:05:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,認識的話就說認識嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.71,0:05:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和她大概有一年沒說過話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.72,0:05:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前參加過同一個課外活動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.22,0:05:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直到去年夏天還好好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.44,0:05:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛? 那種小事就別提了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.06,0:05:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茂木夏樹 這是個好的開端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.51,0:05:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早就看中她 太可愛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.51,0:05:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海 拓海 發什麼呆呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.64,0:05:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不快點就慘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.26,0:05:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一節是文法測驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.29,0:05:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們倆合力買86吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.79,0:05:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打工夠付貸款了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.44,0:05:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要 為什麼那麼拚命想買車?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.54,0:05:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你家不是有車了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.88,0:06:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啊 我老爸的車是自動檔、FF
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.14,0:06:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最要命的是柴油引擎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.73,0:06:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太爛了 那根本不能算車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.44,0:06:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有四個輪胎又能跑的就是輛好車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.24,0:06:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.12,0:06:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跑山道無趣的話就失去了車的意義了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.03,0:06:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼要跑山道?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.48,0:06:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還用說嗎? 為了攻克彎道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.96,0:06:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彎道? 那很有趣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.20,0:06:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然有趣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.23,0:06:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不覺得作為男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.07,0:06:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要很帥地攻克彎道才行嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.13,0:06:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經很厭倦這個了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.61,0:06:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.74,0:06:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們上個月才考到駕照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.97,0:07:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真可愛 夏樹還是穿制服的樣子最漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.22,0:07:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎? 謝謝爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.49,0:07:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 爸爸 我同年級的男孩在打工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.11,0:07:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他暑假里一直工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.08,0:07:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也才十二萬左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.97,0:07:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多就這麼多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.82,0:07:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賺錢還真不容易呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.22,0:07:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和爸爸一個月見三次面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.34,0:07:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就能拿到三十萬...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.48,0:07:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿那麼多沒問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.20,0:07:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題啊 這點價值夏樹當然有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.10,0:07:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎? 我不太明白...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.44,0:07:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.00,0:08:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海 剛才說的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.77,0:08:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,買86吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.49,0:08:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了吧 什麼86...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.85,0:08:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們的眼光不錯嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.15,0:08:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看準了86
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.92,0:08:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吧? 是吧? 是吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.71,0:08:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,池谷前輩也這麼想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.14,0:08:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,86是輛好車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.65,0:08:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞧瞧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.05,0:08:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可實際上我並不清楚86是怎樣的車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.48,0:08:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那車是哪兒造的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.65,0:08:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開玩笑嗎? 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.39,0:08:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你小子想嘗嘗高辛烷汽油嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.34,0:08:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在加油站打工居然不知道86
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.54,0:08:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不覺得丟人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.84,0:08:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不能怪他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.49,0:08:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,92出售時你們也不過小學二 三年級
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.67,0:08:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過我家也有輛做生意的舊車...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.67,0:08:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別把它們混為一談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.50,0:08:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是舊車 86也是與眾不同的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.09,0:08:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我如果買了86
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.78,0:08:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能加入池谷前輩的車隊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.24,0:08:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直很嚮往秋名的SPEED STARS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.40,0:09:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說起來 今天是星期六
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.62,0:09:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到了晚上大家都會齊集秋名山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.97,0:09:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們也來吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.27,0:09:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.98,0:09:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可我們沒車...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.41,0:09:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我開你們去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.05,0:09:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乘前輩的S13?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.51,0:09:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去 去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.62,0:09:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定去 拓海也去的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.54,0:09:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千載難逢的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.76,0:09:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可沒說要去啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.90,0:09:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能見到SPEED STARS的隊員了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.51,0:09:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.47,0:09:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那八點在公交車站接你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.43,0:09:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.28,0:09:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真有空啊 去哪裏的山道?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.01,0:09:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,店長 這附近值得跑的也只有秋名山了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.12,0:09:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管怎樣 我的車隊揚言過要成為秋名山最快的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.54,0:09:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自稱秋名山最快的人遍地都是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.19,0:09:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我當年賽車時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.11,0:10:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有位全體公認的秋名山最快車手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.82,0:10:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且他現在還在跑秋名山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.55,0:10:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在還在?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.16,0:10:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,秋名山的車手我差不多都認識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.00,0:10:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有一位是上了年紀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.79,0:10:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是因為和你們跑的時間段不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.56,0:10:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他現在是豆腐店的老闆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.10,0:10:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凌晨四點載著豆腐送去秋名湖畔的酒店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.65,0:10:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下山時的速度值得一看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.54,0:10:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為做生意無論雨雪每天都開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.33,0:10:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對秋名山道上每個柏油斑點都瞭如指掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.93,0:10:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我敢打賭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.26,0:10:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,秋名山下山最快的一定是豆腐店的86
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.51,0:10:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,豆腐店的86?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.11,0:10:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要出去嗎? 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.46,0:10:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和樹約好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.11,0:11:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晚上去哪我不管 但還是要早起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.55,0:11:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用天天說我也知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.27,0:11:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.16,0:11:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.67,0:11:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會影響池谷前輩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.18,0:11:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不想這樣 但實在太可怕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.68,0:11:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別怪他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.10,0:11:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管誰坐在車手的車上都會嚇得發抖的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.08,0:11:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接著就是二檔的發卡彎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.35,0:11:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真吵啊 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.90,0:11:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 今晚去挑戰 好 那出發吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.96,0:11:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事吧? 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.61,0:12:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到你會那麼害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.11,0:12:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一興奮就只顧猛衝了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.67,0:12:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真丟臉 拓海 像個鄉巴佬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.11,0:12:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐過山車也會大喊大叫的那種人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.84,0:12:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒覺得坐過山車會害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.81,0:12:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是不一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.21,0:12:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,樹 就算解釋了你也肯定不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.64,0:12:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種恐怖感...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.87,0:12:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這群人從沒見過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.88,0:12:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這時候上秋名山?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.98,0:12:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今晚的山道肯定很亂吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.32,0:13:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒見過的傢伙們...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.22,0:13:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,REDSUNS?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.90,0:13:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個被稱為赤城最快的REDSUNS?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.19,0:13:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是赤城REDSUNS車隊的成員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.27,0:13:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恕我冒昧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.64,0:13:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能告訴我這山道最快的車隊或車手是誰嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.98,0:13:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是秋名的SPEED STARS車隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.29,0:14:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是這裏最快的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.70,0:14:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我就長話短說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.41,0:14:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能在這秋名山和我們車隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.51,0:14:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赤城的REDSUNS來場交流會嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.96,0:14:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下好看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.03,0:14:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.40,0:14:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只和本地車手跑毫無新鮮感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.98,0:14:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和外面的車隊比賽的話更刺激吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.02,0:14:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為不僅能交到朋友 交換情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.76,0:14:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還能提高自己的技術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.12,0:14:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先來個熱身運動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.78,0:14:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後派出各自的代表進行上下山的比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.37,0:14:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論輸贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.38,0:14:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,車隊間的和睦才是最終目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.25,0:14:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.54,0:14:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然你那麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.82,0:14:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也沒有理由拒絕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.67,0:14:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就定在下星期六的十點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.22,0:14:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.92,0:14:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天就讓我們好好開一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.81,0:14:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太棒了 太棒了 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.56,0:15:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼好怕的 我們也上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.05,0:15:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,池谷前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.80,0:15:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我見識一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.46,0:15:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被稱為赤城最快的高橋兄弟的車技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.88,0:15:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高橋兄弟 就是雜誌上登載的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.87,0:15:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那兩個超有名的車手?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.34,0:15:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被人稱為轉子的高橋兄弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.02,0:15:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,池谷前輩 我們呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.04,0:15:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思 我認真跑的時候不乘別人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.35,0:15:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等在這裏 過會來接你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.44,0:16:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太悲慘了 為什麼只有我們沒車啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.05,0:16:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,樹 賽車那麼有趣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.67,0:16:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不可思議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.56,0:16:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼會吸引那麼多人呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.03,0:16:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,覺得不可思議的應該是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.20,0:16:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽著逐漸提升至全油門的引擎聲...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.22,0:16:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不覺得熱血沸騰嗎? 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.82,0:16:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,熱血沸騰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.23,0:16:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是藤原豆腐店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.50,0:16:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛 是祐一啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.86,0:16:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吹的什麼風啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.98,0:16:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼啊 好久沒通電話就這麼冷淡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.81,0:16:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先前見到你送貨回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.70,0:16:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給你信號居然無視於我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.18,0:16:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你弄錯了 不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.16,0:16:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會錯 是你的86
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.32,0:16:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.22,0:17:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我的車 但開車的不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.33,0:17:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在送豆腐去酒店的是我兒子拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.74,0:17:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼? 何時開始的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.42,0:17:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五年前開始的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.24,0:17:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五年前? 不就是中學一年級時嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.58,0:17:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡 完全跟不上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.87,0:17:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好快 我已經盡全力跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.33,0:17:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻連REDSUNS的一輛車都追不上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.53,0:17:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣? 大哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.89,0:18:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是些垃圾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.60,0:18:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊裏的候補車手都能輕鬆獲勝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.34,0:18:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下星期不用來最強陣容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.81,0:18:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.35,0:18:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大哥不來的話我也不用來了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.99,0:18:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 你要來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.93,0:18:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,創造出本地人幾年都破不了的賽道紀錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.17,0:18:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.49,0:18:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赤城REDSUNS這名字就無法成為傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.85,0:18:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先我們要改寫縣內所有的賽道紀錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.15,0:18:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總有一天 要在崎玉、神奈川、東京、千葉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.45,0:18:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在整個關東留下最快紀錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.36,0:18:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成為傳說的車手後再引退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.51,0:18:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是赤城REDSUNS的關東最快計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.10,0:19:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厲害 和他們有天壤之別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.88,0:19:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主場被超乎想像地擊敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.99,0:19:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是個巨大的打擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.86,0:19:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靠錢砸出來的懸掛能完全發揮出馬力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.49,0:19:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和REDSUNS競爭實在太勉強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.03,0:19:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但主場作戰也不能退縮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.20,0:19:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊 答應了就必須戰鬥到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.54,0:19:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但只憑耐力是贏不了他們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.57,0:19:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.37,0:19:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.99,0:19:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天很晚了 明天再找地方集合討論吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.40,0:19:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大多車手都不喜歡輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.19,0:19:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下意識地會很好勝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.06,0:19:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼比主場作戰失敗更丟臉的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.29,0:19:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是車手間不成文的共識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.92,0:19:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,涼介呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.69,0:19:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大哥自己先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.40,0:20:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的只有我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.81,0:20:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上就拂曉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.00,0:20:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也差不多該撤了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.89,0:20:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,稍一認真就追不上來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.49,0:20:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們還是太嫩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.85,0:20:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.96,0:20:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是我們車隊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.20,0:20:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是MR2?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.05,0:20:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是180?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.97,0:20:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來得正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.40,0:20:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩個彎就讓你從後視鏡裏消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.88,0:21:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然是86!? 開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.94,0:21:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,舊式的86想超過我的FD?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.94,0:21:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在做惡夢嗎? 可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.36,0:21:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可是赤城REDSUNS的NO.2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.65,0:21:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙不熟悉前面?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.64,0:21:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這淺右彎後是個急左彎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.20,0:21:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不減速的話就會直衝谷底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.73,0:22:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早說過 速度太快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.84,0:22:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有減速的餘地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.14,0:22:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.13,0:22:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慣性漂移...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.30,0:24:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,漂移迷及各位86的車主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:28.30,0:24:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓大家久等啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:30.00,0:24:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,頭文字D終於開場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.60,0:24:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海用點六升無渦輪的86
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.20,0:24:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,窮追猛打三百五十匹馬力高潛力FD...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:38.60,0:24:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的超級漂移技術感覺如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:41.40,0:24:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然是最棒的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.70,0:24:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,懂行的人自然看得懂這充滿特色的頭文字D
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.10,0:24:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下回也能見到火暴的飆車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.80,0:24:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別錯過

